SCHEMA: universe/boundary_model.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.universe.boundary_model
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define universe boundary topology and flux allowance contracts.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record boundary_model
  required:
    - boundary_model_id: id
    - universe_type: enum(closed|open|procedural_infinite)
    - allow_boundary_flux: bool
    - extensions: map
